- I forgot.
- You forgot!

346
00:15:39,400 --> 00:15:44,640
Nevermind. Let's eat next because you did your best.
It's okay, okay.

347
00:15:45,900 --> 00:15:49,620
- Today I did my best, cheers.
- Cheers.

