369
00:17:03,120 --> 00:17:05,960
Yuuta.

370
00:17:05,960 --> 00:17:09,020
He's been ignoring his mother lately.

371
00:17:09,480 --> 00:17:14,160
When it comes to picking oranges it's best to ask grandpa who knows everything about it.

372
00:17:14,260 --> 00:17:15,820
Yuuta.

