00:17:54,220 --> 00:17:55,760
Yes, by yourself.

385
00:17:55,440 --> 00:17:58,740
The errand entails heading home and making orange juice.

386
00:17:58,740 --> 00:18:01,340
Putting the oranges he harvested in the bag.

387
00:18:03,980 --> 00:18:06,100
- Remember to make orange juice.
- Yep.

388
00:18:06,100 --> 00:18:08,100
Go home by yourself and make it.

389
00:18:08,100 --> 00:18:10,100
Yes.

390
00:18:12,160 --> 00:18:15,540
For the mother who thinks that he never listens to her

