00:18:15,540 --> 00:18:18,920
it's a bit unusual how fast he took off.

392
00:18:20,580 --> 00:18:21,780
He left.

393
00:18:21,780 --> 00:18:24,560
He does what he is told. When it comes to it.

394
00:18:25,800 --> 00:18:28,040
I'm so relieved.

395
00:18:28,040 --> 00:18:30,040
Will he come back again?

396
00:18:30,040 --> 00:18:34,040
Yep, he will be back. After finishing his errand.

397
00:18:34,680 --> 00:18:38,040
The mother trusts Yuuta.

398
00:18:38,040 --> 00:18:40,040
I'm so relieved.

399
00:18:42,040 --> 00:18:45,900
She's so overwhelmed by how well-behaved his response was.

400
00:18:45,900 --> 00:18:47,900
He listened to his mother.

401
00:18:47,900 --> 00:18:49,900
You are making me cry as well.

402
00:18:52,160 --> 00:18:53,860
Since this is my first time...

403
00:18:53,860 --> 00:18:55,600
I was a bit uneasy but...

404
00:18:55,600 --> 00:19:00,320
since he left he didn't need to look back even once so...

405
00:19:00,320 --> 00:19:02,320
so... so...

406
00:19:02,320 --> 00:19:04,900
I feel so lonely.

407
00:19:05,320 --> 00:19:08,220
It's too good to be true. I see.

408
00:19:08,220 --> 00:19:12,420
Once he is home there are games and and a TV.
