00:19:22,120 --> 00:19:25,120
They are all the work of Yuuta.

413
00:19:31,440 --> 00:19:34,560
We thought that he would start playing as soon as he got home.

414
00:19:34,560 --> 00:19:37,680
But these are the instruments for making orange juice.

415
00:19:38,120 --> 00:19:40,620
I'm sorry. I was talking nonsense.

416
00:19:40,620 --> 00:19:43,560
He came back to properly do his job.

417
00:19:43,860 --> 00:19:46,480
Things surely change when you become 4.

418
00:19:48,060 --> 00:19:50,620
What? Did you forget something?

419
00:19:52,840 --> 00:19:55,620
He's leaving for something.

420
00:19:58,100 --> 00:20:00,680
Hold up, that face.

421
00:20:03,280 --> 00:20:05,020
Just as I thought.

422
00:20:07,280 --> 00:20:09,380
He found a neighborhood friend.

423
00:20:10,340 --> 00:20:12,400
It's Maro!

424
00:20:15,440 --> 00:20:18,360
The play is escalating.

425
00:20:19,580 --> 00:20:21,320
Where did it go?

426
00:20:21,320 --> 00:20:24,660
What happened to coming back after pressing the juice?

427
00:20:27,240 --> 00:20:29,300
Seems like there will be none of that.

428
00:20:31,540 --> 00:20:32,780
Waiting for 40 minutes.

429
00:20:32,780 --> 00:20:34,520
Poor mom.

430
00:20:33,940 --> 00:20:35,920
He isn't back yet.

431
00:20:36,660 --> 00:20:39,040
It sure takes a long time.

432
00:20:40,540 --> 00:20:42,380
Let's take a break.

433
00:20:42,380 --> 00:20:44,380
He isn't very useful.

434
00:20:45,400 --> 00:20:47,640
I'm worried cause we don't know how he is.

435
00:20:47,640 --> 00:20:51,240
The only one who knows how he is is Maro.

436
00:20:55,360 --> 00:20:58,240
Close to an hour has passed.

437
00:20:58,240 --> 00:21:01,280
- He isn't pressing juice.
- He forgot all about it.

438
00:21:00,380 --> 00:21:02,840
He's back again.

439
00:21:02,840 --> 00:21:06,260
He's playing by himself. I wonder if he will press the juice.

440
00:21:09,180 --> 00:21:13,860
What!? You only came to take your hat?
