441
00:21:13,860 --> 00:21:15,560
And at that time...

442
00:21:17,660 --> 00:21:19,240
The phone is ringing.

443
00:21:21,600 --> 00:21:24,840
He loves to answer the phone.

444
00:21:26,520 --> 00:21:28,020
Hello.

445
00:21:28,020 --> 00:21:29,720
Yuuta, it's your mother.

446
00:21:29,720 --> 00:21:33,260
Yuuta, how is the juice coming along?

447
00:21:33,900 --> 00:21:36,220
Still.. It's already finished.

448
00:21:36,220 --> 00:21:38,840
Still... Finished??

