457
00:21:53,000 --> 00:21:55,500
- Yep.
- Hurry up and bring it with you.

458
00:21:55,640 --> 00:21:57,820
- Yes.
- Yes, I'm counting on you.

459
00:22:01,320 --> 00:22:03,220
The answer was good but...

460
00:22:03,220 --> 00:22:06,220
He said that he has made it.

461
00:22:06,220 --> 00:22:08,220
- He said he's made it?
- Yep.

462
00:22:08,220 --> 00:22:12,040
Since he said he's already made it he better hurry.

463
00:22:12,840 --> 00:22:15,560
Hey, you can't stand on the place where you eat food.

464
00:22:18,140 --> 00:22:19,480
It's onigiri.

465
00:22:18,520 --> 00:22:23,020
Mother has left it for lunch for when they get back.

466
00:22:24,100 --> 00:22:27,040
- Because he ran.
- Yeah, must be hungry.

467
00:22:28,400 --> 00:22:31,100
He started eating it.

468
00:22:31,100 --> 00:22:33,100
Something is different about it.

469
00:22:33,100 --> 00:22:35,240
Yuuta has noticed something.

470
00:22:36,220 --> 00:22:38,780
Yuuta who is afraid of ghosts.

471
00:22:38,780 --> 00:22:41,660
He's never been home alone before.

472
00:22:41,660 --> 00:22:44,420
- What's wrong?
- He's hiding in a cool place.

473
00:22:47,680 --> 00:22:51,260
Oh right! Mom can't yell at me.

474
00:22:54,160 --> 00:22:58,880
It seems he can break higher things as he gets taller.

475
00:22:58,440 --> 00:23:00,300
Amazing.

476
00:23:01,640 --> 00:23:04,460
What? He's taking the water gun.

477
00:23:04,460 --> 00:23:07,000
What about pressing the juice?

478
00:23:07,000 --> 00:23:10,060
Maro, you are in danger. Run away.

479
00:23:16,360 --> 00:23:19,060
Amazing timing.

480
00:23:19,520 --> 00:23:21,520
Perfect timing.

481
00:23:21,520 --> 00:23:24,520
It's as if his mother is watching him.

482
00:23:24,900 --> 00:23:25,900
What?

483
00:23:25,900 --> 00:23:27,900
Hello. Yuuta?

484
00:23:28,160 --> 00:23:29,800
This is your mother.

485
00:23:30,140 --> 00:23:33,280
Hurry up, press the juice and bring it.

486
00:23:33,280 --> 00:23:34,160
Yes.

487
00:23:34,160 --> 00:23:36,940
And what about your protection charm?

488
00:23:35,980 --> 00:23:37,960
The protection charm? It's there.

489
00:23:37,960 --> 00:23:39,780
Do you have it on you?

490
00:23:39,780 --> 00:23:40,620
Yes.

491
00:23:40,620 --> 00:23:43,880
Lies. I can see that you don't have it on.

492
00:23:43,880 --> 00:23:44,840
She can see?

493
00:23:44,840 --> 00:23:46,840
Be sure to wear it.

