507
00:24:26,620 --> 00:24:28,400
Can't be helped. Let's do it.

508
00:24:29,400 --> 00:24:32,040
He usually is happy to help make the juice.

509
00:24:32,040 --> 00:24:34,920
That's why the mother has chosen this to be the errand.

510
00:24:35,200 --> 00:24:38,800
He's a child who doesn't do what he doesn't want to. But does the things he loves.

